              <div class="mt-6">
                  <div class="">
                      <div class="flex mb-1">
                          <p class="text-gray-300 mr-2">
                              <span class="border rounded-full material-icons p-1" style="font-size:10px">
                                  done</span>
                          </p>
                          <p class="text-gray-300"> Select a template from our library of
                            professional designs</p>
                      </div>
                      <div class="flex mb-1">
                          <p class="text-gray-300 mr-2">
                              <span class="border rounded-full material-icons p-1" style="font-size:10px">
                                  done</span>
                          </p>
                          <p class="text-gray-300">Build your resume with our
                            industry-specific bullet points</p>
                      </div>
                      <div class="flex mb-1">
                          <p class="text-gray-300 mr-2">
                              <span class="border rounded-full material-icons p-1" style="font-size:10px">
                                  done</span>
                          </p>
                          <p class="text-gray-300">Download your resume, print it out
                            and get it ready to send!</p>
                      </div>
                  </div>
              </div>
              
              <hr class="border-1 border-gray-500 my-10">
              <div class="mt-6 text-gray-400 font-light">
                After creating the resume you would feel the Attractive Professional skills mentioned in your CV and Internships which you have been experienced and more.
              </div>
             
          </div>
      </div>
       </div>
